{"id":142236,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：bp丢失索赔者个人资料/","date":"2011-03-31T11:00:47Z","modified":"2011-03-31T11:00:47Z","title":"简讯：BP丢失索赔者个人资料","content":"<div>\n<p>英国石油公司(BP)说，公司一名雇员丢失一部手提电脑，里面有去年墨西哥湾漏油事件数千名索赔者的个人资料。</p>\n<p>这些资料包括路易斯安那州索赔居民的姓名，地址和社会保险号码。</p>\n<p>英国石油公司对这起丢失资料事件表示遗憾，并说没有迹象显示丢失的资料遭到滥用。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/K49yX-WNsX2AAw4LBLA-10dw154/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/K49yX-WNsX2AAw4LBLA-10dw154/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/K49yX-WNsX2AAw4LBLA-10dw154/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/K49yX-WNsX2AAw4LBLA-10dw154/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/sG5nv0pAHCA\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):fanqiangyakexi1ATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}